Line with Focus Chart
---------------------

```{r nvd3-line-with-focus}
ecm <- reshape2::melt(
  economics[,c('date', 'uempmed', 'psavert')], 
  id = 'date'
)
p7 <- nPlot(value ~ date, group = 'variable', 
  data = ecm, 
  type = 'lineWithFocusChart'
)
p7
```

